msgid ""
"<1.so>...<2.te_si>Seriously?<3.pa><4.te_si>\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<5.so>Well...<6.pa>I suppose there are a lot of\n"
"crazy things in this world that are\n"
"hard to grasp.\n"
"Oh, my name's Lasli. I run a clothing\n"
"shop in the village with my older sister,\n"
"Claree. You should stop by sometime."
msgstr ""

